}

docs {
  ## Get Recipe Equipment by ID
  ดึงข้อมูลอุปกรณ์ทำอาหารเดียวตาม ID สำหรับติดตามอุปกรณ์ที่จำเป็นในการเตรียมสูตรอาหาร

  Retrieves a specific kitchen equipment definition (e.g., oven, mixer, blender) that can be associated with recipes.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Recipe equipment ID |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  > Permission key not found in seed; review needed.

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "code": "EQ-001",
      "name": "Commercial Oven",
      "description": "Large capacity commercial oven",
      "category_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "brand": "Rational",
      "model": "SCC-61",
      "is_active": true,
      "info": [],
      "audit": {
        "created_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
        "created_by": { "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890", "name": "John Doe" },
        "updated_at": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z",
        "updated_by": { "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567891", "name": "Jane Smith" },
        "deleted_at": null,
        "deleted_by": null
      }
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 404 | Recipe equipment not found |
}

